{"tid":154992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿拉斯加發現新油田 美國30年來陸上最大規模","createTime":"2017-03-13T16:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T04:13:53.000Z","uid":60545,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd5e8e6a4045a4f48bdd09eea62113bb0b2965b","tid":154992,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:44:43.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕阿拉斯加州是美國第三大產油州，有外媒報導指出，西班牙能源公司Repsol於9日宣布，他們在阿拉斯加北坡（North Slope）發現了一座蘊藏12億桶石油的巨大油田，是美國30年來發現最大的陸上油田。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，這座油田位於阿拉斯加北坡的Nuiqsut村落附近，是由西班牙能源公司Repsol所發現，油田的土地則是由阿姆斯壯公司（Armstrong）自2001年起開始承租。這座油田將於2021年開始初步投產，預計1天可生產12萬桶原油，年產量將近4、5千萬桶。<br />\n<br />\n阿拉斯加在1980年代的石油產量高達每天200萬桶，目前每天只有生產約60萬桶，如今又再發現這座巨大油田，各界預估將能帶動阿拉斯加的能源產量。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2002311\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2002311&d=59R0jsXjdYUW2Qgfgwt6uNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=aa19909f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2002311&h=a5aca344\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2002311</a>"},{"pid":"743f10ae9b5d4ab2276bb288f5fc5ed7698091a8","tid":154992,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:45:48.000Z","msg":"俄佬玩完？"},{"pid":"d794681635eb203797bf5a96c9a880358049bfa0","tid":154992,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:47:20.000Z","msg":"小學個陣:全球石油將於50年內用完<br />\n<br />\n大學畢業:油價再創新低<br />\n<br />\n個仔讀小學:又發現某某地底有油"},{"pid":"d58c9b260a8be253805fa5b5eb2bd8a11a98c129","tid":154992,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:47:58.000Z","msg":"俄佬當年賣阿拉斯加賣左幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36120db1ad2e2b023ea0491019bfac7f56f1806","tid":154992,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:53:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俄佬當年賣